column5: Master Suite w/bath, walkin closet, cafe table. 3 mi.from White Rock Lake, 4 mi.from Dallas Arboretum & Botanical Gardens w/Concerts, close to Casa Linda restaurants, shops & movies, many things 2 do. Downtown (9 mi). Elite Northpark mall and Galleria mall near by: 6/8 miles away. Airprt: DFW/LOVE. Ask about airport rides!! Amenities: laundry room, kitchen & backyard oasis!!
column8: Master Suite Gem Dallas ~ home access
